\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Yes, I couldn't tell - just coppers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Was it a regular thing that you got on a particular day of the week?
