remember anyone helping except probably when might have midwife would come in when the children were born and just stay until such times as - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2260340\charrsid4933843 well}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
