\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Well it was at home - there was no hospitals then but - children were born at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Who looked after the family then?
