\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Yes, they had Irish friends and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Who were living in Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 When would they have seen them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 
Well, we lived down in the Old Swan and they lived in Wavertree district so it would be a couple of miles and of course it was across country so there wasn't the transport like they have today 
so you'd walk to the house and meet - meet them you see and - and have tea with them and a chat and that and then - we'd come home We didn't stay late I mean you'd be home by ten o'clock because dad had to be up early in the morning to go to work so we ha
d to get back - yes. So occasionally we'd go and visit friends like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Would they come to you?
