Oh they'd come yes - and then it - you see, with being from Ireland they'd have a chat about - my parents said home, to them Ireland was home you see and it - they'd jaw all about the neighbours and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Would you say your parents shared their friends or did they have their own special friends?
