hem because we looked on ourselves were Irish folk and - father knew them from home - he would visit them on account. And there was something I was going to mention about it - something that came to my mind then. Funny how - yes, yes. What would I be - oh
, I remember when the - Coronation of Kind Edward. Now that's going back a long time - let's say 1902. About 1902. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2260340\charrsid4933843 
