tery it was held - Wavertree Park here and they had this show an and going along and it was a lovely summers day and meeting these two ladies that come over from Ireland aft - who afterwards one }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8812530 Married}{
