ut to work so she joined the Inland Revenue and she had a pension from the Inland Revenue, she did about twenty years with them but unfortunately she was - I must say she was a smoker - and whether that had anything to do with it - but - unfortunately she
 died just recently and - the two girls lived together - they didn't marry and - it was a big blow to Ann which is the oldest she's still living. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 
