\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 No, oh no, no. But - person - you might go to a house where they had a piano which is - only very occasionally.
