\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7166200 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Well, with the boys as I tol
