hen as - in the sorting office. You had to start up and learn everything from the very beginning so - I was in the sorting office for - oh, several years before I - I came on to writing }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5572670\charrsid4933843 duties
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843  and then - I was in pretty well all the branches - the first bra
