cal side. I did take a little active interest because - I found - I found that you had to take part in something or other if you wanted to - come under notice, in other words, if you - if you just went along as an ordinary person say oh well he's no inter
est you see. So I was on the central committee of the Union but in those days the Union hadn't the force it has today. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5572670\charrsid4933843 
