\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9197408 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6837232\charrsid4933843 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
